reviewText: Our first video was very low budget. We are a non-profit organization with the mission to end obesity in the church. our next video will be moderate budget with the theme of war against the spirit of obesity!!! Your tax deductible donations make this happen!! Please come to our website and become a sponsor. Highest Praise Dance Fitness dot com. We have our 501(c)(3). Thanks

The DVD is very low budget.  The workout routines are not routines,  it's just a bunch of people attempting to exercise. It's like catching a YouTube video.  I applaud their efforts, but this DVD should not be for sale.
